item.title: CVE-2022-4714|2024-08-03T01:48:40.301Z -- unknown -- wp%20dark%20mode
item.description: The WP Dark Mode WordPress plugin before 4.0.0 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack
